#use wml::debian::translation-check translation="1.1"

<P>如果你正在考慮銷售 Debian 光碟，請查看\
<a href="info">銷售商須知</a>網頁。

<p>If you would like to be added to this page,
請以<strong>英文</strong>寄電子郵件至
<A href="mailto:cdvendors@debian.org">cdvendors@debian.org</A>. With the
following details:
<UL>
<li>銷售商名字 (Vendor Name)
<li>銷售商的網址 (URL of Vendor)
<li>Whether or not you donate some of the sale to Debian
<li>Type of CDs sold (see at the top of page for details)
<li>所在的國家 (Country you are in)
<li>Do you ship orders overseas ("yes", "no", "some areas" or "within Europe")
<li>URL of a web page that has information about your Debian CDs
<li>Email address for sales enquiries
<li>What architectures your CDs are for.
</ul>

<P>  
It is important that you keep this information up to date. We try to check
the vendor sites every now and then and if, for example, the web page no longer
exists or mail bounces, we delete that entry.
<P>
You must have a webpage (specified by the 'Debian URL' line) that
mentions the Debian CDs you sell. This entry is mandatory if you want to
be listed on our site.
